data.description: Situated on a large corner lot, this charming Cape Cod style home is conveniently located near shopping, dining, the interstate and bases. Immediately upon entry you are welcomed into the light filled living room which features stunning custom tile work and a cozy wood burning fireplace perfect for cold winter nights. With a floor plan that is ideal for entertaining, the dining room is tucked between the living room and kitchen and even includes access to the fully fenced in backyard which features a patio and plenty of room for a fire pit. The kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances and a beautiful backsplash. The downstairs bedroom includes a large walk-in closet and is located just across the hall from a full bathroom. Upstairs you'll find two additional bedrooms, a full bathroom and a bonus room which could make a great playroom, office, exercise room or even an additional bedroom. New carpet was installed just before hitting the market. Some photos feature virtual staging.
